Connect the server...

Set profile...
	Nickname
	
List all rooms...
	Public chat
		the number of people: unlimited
		joining: open
		name: Welcome to the pubilc room!
	Group chat
		the number of people: to be set
		joining: to be set(blocked/open/apply)
		name: to be set
	Private chat
		the number of people: 2
		joining: blocked
		name: [the nickname of creator]'s room
		
List all people...
	Nickname
	Room each person in
		
Join a room.../Join a person...

Create a room...
	1. choose type
	2. configure
		for Group chat, set the limited number & joining state & room name
		for Private chat, invite the other person by Nickname
	3. join the room
